<p>Y‚Äôknow how the YouTube algorithm is <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/2/11/18220379/youtube-creator-burnout-elle-mills-algorithm">an awful garbage fire</a> but sometimes it serves you a gem that feels like a piece of yourself in a time capsule? That‚Äôs what this video is for me.</p>

